classic hunting game With Pygame
============================

Overview
--------
classic hunt shoot is a remake of the classic game written in Python with Pygame.


Installation
------------
Pygame must be installed first. For installing pygame on system for the current user
> python3 -m pip install -U pygame --user

To run the game, simply type:
> python3 hunt.py

Controls
--------
- Use the mouse to aim and shoot
- 's' toggles sound
- 'Esc' quits the game
